  <version>SUSE Rancher Prime: Continuous Delivery (Fleet)</version>
  <descriptions treatment="append">
    <desc lang="en-us">
        <p>
          SUSE Rancher Prime: Continuous Delivery is a set of Kubernetes custom
          resource definitions (CRDs) and controllers that manage GitOps for a
          single Kubernetes cluster or a large scale deployment of Kubernetes
          clusters. It is a distributed initialization system that makes it
          easy to customize applications and manage HA clusters from a single
          point.
        </p>
      </desc>
  </descriptions>
